.TH "_ctl_ioctl_main" 9 "_ctl_ioctl_main" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
_ctl_ioctl_main \- main ioctl entry point
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "long" _ctl_ioctl_main
.BI "(struct file *file "  ","
.BI "unsigned int cmd "  ","
.BI "void __user *arg "  ","
.BI "u8 compat "  ","
.BI "u16 mpi_version "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "file" 12
(struct file)
.IP "cmd" 12
ioctl opcode
.IP "arg" 12
user space data buffer
.IP "compat" 12
handles 32 bit applications in 64bit os
.IP "mpi_version" 12
will be MPI2_VERSION for mpt2ctl ioctl device &
MPI25_VERSION | MPI26_VERSION for mpt3ctl ioctl device.
